  "name": "RPlog_Convoy_Lost",
  "title": "Convoy Lost",
  "summary": "A New Republic task force led by Gren Delede aboard the Eternal Vigilance, with Mon Calamari cruisers, the corvette Diligence under Twila, and four starfighter squadrons including Kyrin Sh'vani's Ghosts, ambushes an Imperial convoy of two Neutron Star bulk cruisers and eight transports. Imperial Marshal Krieg, commanding from Captain Keline's bridge, scrambles fighters and personally sorties in his TIE to renew a grudge match with the Ghost pilots Lance 'Wildman' Corbet and Raxis 'Raptor' L'ygr. The capital ships slug it out as B-wings batter the cruisers' shields, the Diligence is forced to retreat and dock, and the dogfight narrows to a duel between Krieg and the two Ghosts. Krieg disables Raxis's X-wing, forcing him to eject into the void, but the New Republic captures the disabled freighters and their cargo. The Imperials evacuate one crippled bulk cruiser and jump the other out to Carida, having lost eight freighters and a cruiser while bloodying their attackers.",
